<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(خ م)</span> , وَعَنْ ابْنِ عُمَرَ - رضي الله عنهما -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> (<span class="c1">" نَهَى يَوْمَ خَيْبَرَ عَنْ لُحُومِ الْحُمُرِ الْأَهْلِيَّةِ "</span>) <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(وَكَانَ النَّاسُ احْتَاجُوا إِلَيْهَا)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
